record.text: Awesome! Sorry for interrupting your fun. I look forward to chatting with you again soon.
I saw a video of Conor McGregor having a conversation on Youtube and it was a great conversation. Do you know the Capcom game Street Fighter?
Wow! You also like pro wrestling. I've never watched it, but I know Conor McGregor. Is he a popular fighter in Ireland?
It's the middle of the night there right now, isn't it? Are you still awake?
私も数年前に骨折で一週間ほど入院した経験があるので、お気持ちとっても分かります。お大事になさって下さい🥺
Thank you very much. I look forward to speaking with you again.🤗
I see! You posted about a game console that reminded me of something nostalgic, so I thought I'd like to talk about games someday and I just couldn't resist commenting. Thank you for your time.🥹
That's right! In Japan it's called Super Famicom. By the way, it was released 34 years ago. I thought you wouldn't know what it was when you saw posts about the 64 and DS, but I was surprised.❗👏👏
I've played Mario Kart before. By the way... I'm going to upload a photo now, so please guess what game console the cartridge is for.🤔
What surprised me was that there are Nintendo game consoles in Ireland. Are Japanese games popular?
That's right 😊 Are you from Ireland 🇮🇪?
I think that illustrations are more popular in Japan because anime is so popular. Also, if you want to create a realistic image, why not just use the real thing?
There are many people who create illustrations, but realistic ones are not so popular🥲
I think you'll be even more surprised if you check out my Instagram using the URL in my profile🤭
